This app is made for people who love to play cricket but they don’t get opportunity to do it, so we want to build an web application which provide them a platform where they can enroll themselves for the upcoming matches. At first player with register on the application and create their login and password and will verified by email. If player got verified then they provide their availability to play and their availability will be matched by other players by the scheduler. After this step player will pay their entry fee by credit or debit and all the money will be received by financial department and they will provide all the equipment and provide play ground. Next step will be taking player’s game history and experience which will be evaluated by the system and provide best match according to players capability and create a team for them. After that system will ask for final confirmation for match .
